  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><u>PARKING LOT SIMULATOR: CAR COLLECTOR</u></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Start as a <strong>valet</strong> <u>parking cars</u> and work your way up to becoming a legendary <strong>car collector</strong>! Park customer's vehicles quickly and safely, earn tips, and expand your parking lot to build the most prestigious business in town.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But that’s just the beginning! Use your earnings to buy and customize your dream cars, cruise freely through the city, and enjoy the nightlife. Visit nightclubs, explore the city’s underground car scene, and maybe even test your skills in illegal street races!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>🔥 Key Features:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>🅿️  Build and Manage Your Parking Empire!</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Start from the bottom as a solo valet and work your way up to owning a thriving parking empire! Manage your business, hire employees to park cars for you, and optimize your lot for maximum profits. Expand your operations, unlock new locations, and turn your small parking lot into a luxury car paradise.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Will you run a high-end valet service for the rich, or dominate the underground car scene? The choice is yours!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3628630/extras/a58b4ce66d0b9a301850d7270819d617.poster.avif?t=1744786881\" width=800 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3628630/extras/a58b4ce66d0b9a301850d7270819d617.webm?t=1744786881\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3628630/extras/a58b4ce66d0b9a301850d7270819d617.mp4?t=1744786881\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>🚗 Realistic Valet Experience</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Park customers' cars carefully and provide the best service to maximize your earnings.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3628630/extras/de27c168aa57ba452247dd4e75725d16.poster.avif?t=1744786881\" width=800 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3628630/extras/de27c168aa57ba452247dd4e75725d16.webm?t=1744786881\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3628630/extras/de27c168aa57ba452247dd4e75725d16.mp4?t=1744786881\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>🏎️ Build Your Dream Car Collection</u></strong>From classic beauties to high-performance supercars, collect and customize the cars of your dreams! Buy and sell vehicles to expand your collection, then take them for a spin in the open world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3628630/extras/cf2125de97f4c82d35cc750d33033a63.poster.avif?t=1744786881\" width=800 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3628630/extras/cf2125de97f4c82d35cc750d33033a63.webm?t=1744786881\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3628630/extras/cf2125de97f4c82d35cc750d33033a63.mp4?t=1744786881\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>🛠️ Customization & Tuning & Repair</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Upgrade your rides with  paint jobs and performance tuning to make each car truly your own.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>🌆 FreeRoam Open-World City Exploration</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Drive freely through the city, visit different locations, and discover hidden opportunities.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>🎉 Nightlife & Luxury Living</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Spend your hard-earned money on high-end entertainment and social events.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step into the <strong>parking business</strong>, master the art of <strong>valet parking</strong>, and rise to the top as a legendary <strong>car collector</strong>!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🚘 Are you ready to build the <strong>parking empire</strong> and <strong>car collection</strong> of your dreams?</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><u>PARKING LOT SIMULATOR: CAR COLLECTOR</u></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Start as a <strong>valet</strong> <u>parking cars</u> and work your way up to becoming a legendary <strong>car collector</strong>! Park customer's vehicles quickly and safely, earn tips, and expand your parking lot to build the most prestigious business in town.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But that’s just the beginning! Use your earnings to buy and customize your dream cars, cruise freely through the city, and enjoy the nightlife. Visit nightclubs, explore the city’s underground car scene, and maybe even test your skills in illegal street races!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>🔥 Key Features:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>🅿️  Build and Manage Your Parking Empire!</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Start from the bottom as a solo valet and work your way up to owning a thriving parking empire! Manage your business, hire employees to park cars for you, and optimize your lot for maximum profits. Expand your operations, unlock new locations, and turn your small parking lot into a luxury car paradise.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Will you run a high-end valet service for the rich, or dominate the underground car scene? The choice is yours!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3628630/extras/a58b4ce66d0b9a301850d7270819d617.poster.avif?t=1744786881\" width=800 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3628630/extras/a58b4ce66d0b9a301850d7270819d617.webm?t=1744786881\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3628630/extras/a58b4ce66d0b9a301850d7270819d617.mp4?t=1744786881\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>🚗 Realistic Valet Experience</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Park customers' cars carefully and provide the best service to maximize your earnings.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3628630/extras/de27c168aa57ba452247dd4e75725d16.poster.avif?t=1744786881\" width=800 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3628630/extras/de27c168aa57ba452247dd4e75725d16.webm?t=1744786881\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3628630/extras/de27c168aa57ba452247dd4e75725d16.mp4?t=1744786881\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>🏎️ Build Your Dream Car Collection</u></strong>From classic beauties to high-performance supercars, collect and customize the cars of your dreams! Buy and sell vehicles to expand your collection, then take them for a spin in the open world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3628630/extras/cf2125de97f4c82d35cc750d33033a63.poster.avif?t=1744786881\" width=800 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3628630/extras/cf2125de97f4c82d35cc750d33033a63.webm?t=1744786881\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3628630/extras/cf2125de97f4c82d35cc750d33033a63.mp4?t=1744786881\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>🛠️ Customization & Tuning & Repair</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Upgrade your rides with  paint jobs and performance tuning to make each car truly your own.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>🌆 FreeRoam Open-World City Exploration</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Drive freely through the city, visit different locations, and discover hidden opportunities.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>🎉 Nightlife & Luxury Living</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Spend your hard-earned money on high-end entertainment and social events.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step into the <strong>parking business</strong>, master the art of <strong>valet parking</strong>, and rise to the top as a legendary <strong>car collector</strong>!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🚘 Are you ready to build the <strong>parking empire</strong> and <strong>car collection</strong> of your dreams?</p>",
